<html lang='en'>

  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Réinitialisation de mot de passe</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: 'Ubuntu'; background-color: #fafafa; padding: 20px; margin: 0; }
      .container { text-align: center; max-width: 636px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 50px 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .logo {
      text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; } .resetPwLink {text-decoration: !important none;
      cursor: pointer;} .logo img { max-width: 250px; height: auto; } .parent-button { width: 100%;
      } .password {font-weight: bold; font-size: 1em; color: black;} .reset-button:hover {
      background-color: #12103be9; } .link { text-decoration: none; color: white !important; }
      .title-message { margin-top: 40px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; color: #272727; }
      .main-content { padding: 0px 50px; } .content { text-align: center; padding: 0px 30px;
      text-wrap: wrap; } .subtitle-message { font-size: 14px; margin: 0px 10%; color: #808080; }
      .footer-message { font-size: 14px; color: #272727; } .footer { width: 100%; position:
      relative; display: flex; justify-content: center; } .rule { width: 364px; height: 2px; border:
      none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 50px; margin-bottom: 30px;
      background-color: #eaeaea; }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='logo'>
        <img
          src='https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/sortlist-core-api/emcnfzmuykxi3lqo1vguxotruwed'
          alt='Logo hairun'
        />
      </div>
      <div class='main-content'>
        <h1 class='title-message'>Cher/Chère {{username}},</h1>
        <div class='content'>
          <p class='subtitle-message'>Votre mot de passe par défaut pour votre compte HaiRun SI est:
            <span class='password'>{{context}}</span></p>

          <p class='subtitle-message'>Mais si vous voulez le réinitialiser
            <a class='resetPwLink' href={{resetPwLink}}>cliquer ici</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <center class='footer'>
        <div class='rule'>
        </div>
      </center>
      <p class='footer-message'>Cordialement,</p>
      <p class='footer-message' style='margin-top: -10px;'>L'équipe HaiRun Technology</p>
    </div>

  </body>

</html>